title: Aaron Lewis - The Road (Deluxe Version) (2012)
description:
The Road, is the debut, full-length studio album by Staind frontman Aaron Lewis. His second country music effort, it was released by Blaster Records on November 13, 2012

All songs written and composed by Aaron Lewis except "Granddaddy's Gun", written by Rhett Akins, Dallas Davidson, and Bobby Pinson.
